    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255860/extras/9618f40453f2d98781cfa776a7779a42.avif?t=1763023138\" width=620 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《海默2000》是一款互动文字解谜游戏。在游戏中，你将扮演回收员弗兰克，深入希望家园的遗址，回收名为“海默2000”的人工智能计算机。你可以自由地与海默对话，而不受限于固定的文本选项，并使用任意关键词检索海默过去的对话记录。80张奇特的“人像”插图散落在希望家园的各个角落，它们串联起一段段无法改变的蒙尘往事，最终解开海默所守护的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255860/extras/8104ab987895cbd7508a07c67230b860.poster.avif?t=1763023138\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255860/extras/8104ab987895cbd7508a07c67230b860.webm?t=1763023138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255860/extras/8104ab987895cbd7508a07c67230b860.mp4?t=1763023138\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255860/extras/2719b1f23c71f7e86bc614a34bc1f680.avif?t=1763023138\" width=620 height=100 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有文本选项的自由对话系统</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以使用任意关键词检索海默过去的对话记录</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由80张奇特的“人脸”插图，串联起一个完整而动人的故事</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基于算法的“粒子”与“音符”等互动小程序</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >仿操作系统的独特界面</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255860/extras/cc3e6305f0222aa84a394fa3c0d12501.poster.avif?t=1763023138\" width=610 height=406 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255860/extras/cc3e6305f0222aa84a394fa3c0d12501.webm?t=1763023138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255860/extras/cc3e6305f0222aa84a394fa3c0d12501.mp4?t=1763023138\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎加入玩家QQ群：469273424</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2>",
